Introducing our powerful browser extension, the ultimate tool for anyone who needs lightning-fast and reliable AI-powered responses from ChatGPT!

Custom features: 
- Add a permanent prompt, ChatGPT will always remember
- Activate translation mode to translate from any language into any language
- Activate grammar mode to improve your spelling and expressions
- Nice mode, when you need a little happiness in your life

With this extension, you can now access the cutting-edge technology of OpenAI directly from your browser. Say goodbye to endlessly searching the web for the answers you need - this extension delivers expert-level assistance in seconds, no matter what you're working on.

Our extension is incredibly user-friendly and intuitive, so you'll be up and running in no time. Simply install it onto your browser, and you'll be able to access the full suite of features that you know and love from chat.openai.com. Whether you're looking for help with natural language processing, data analysis, or anything in between, our extension has you covered.

With its lightning-fast response times and unrivaled accuracy, our extension is perfect for professionals, academics, and anyone who needs the best in AI technology at their fingertips. Don't settle for anything less - install our extension today and take your productivity to the next level!
